{"id":594183,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/08/【网络民议】户籍成为了隔离人民的柏林墙/","date":"2018-08-27T14:56:09Z","modified":"2018-08-27T14:56:09Z","title":"【网络民议】户籍成为了隔离人民的柏林墙","content":"<p>编者按：据澎湃新闻报道，9月1日起，因校舍被腾退，苏州800多名外来务工人员子女被安排到附近公办重点小学，遭重点小学众多家长反对：让非学区的学生抢占了公立学校的资源。小学校长表示，会用铁栅栏等加以“隔离”，独立管理。为此，网民评论， 户籍成为了隔离人民的柏林墙。</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-594184\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/1-53.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"338\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/1-53.jpg 440w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/1-53-300x203.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-594185\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/2-44.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"500\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/2-44.jpg 440w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/2-44-150x150.jpg 150w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/2-44-300x300.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/2-44-70x70.jpg 70w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/2-44-50x50.jpg 50w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-594186\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/3-37.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"674\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/3-37.jpg 440w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/3-37-223x300.jpg 223w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-594187\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/4-34.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"672\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/4-34.jpg 440w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/4-34-223x300.jpg 223w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<blockquote><p><strong>以下为中国数字时代编辑摘